#id=1
#text=My parents had purchased a new lemon tree that they wanted to plant , so I went to their house to help them plant it .
#id=2
#text=My dad already had a place picked out to put the tree , so we went to work .
#id=3
#text=We had to dig a fairly large hole and it took several hours .
#id=4
#text=We had to take a break half way through because it was rather tiring .
#id=5
#text=After the water break , we finished digging and we tested the depth by setting the bundled roots into the hole to make sure that it was deep enough .
#id=6
#text=Since it was , I added some of the nutrient rich soil additives into the bottom of the hole and my dad watered the soil additives with the garden hose .
#id=7
#text=We then cut the burlap off that had covered the roots and carefully set the tree into the hole .
#id=8
#text=We took another break and then set in to refilling the hole with dirt .
#id=9
#text=It took a long time to do , but it was well worth it .
#text=I left the hose turned on at the base of the tree so that it could get properly soaked and we went back into the house to properly cool off .
